info.description:
# 26 Keras Models List 

## about

A package of Python to training any dataset with any keras models in 26 models list 
This repo aims at providing both reusable Keras Models and pre-trained models, which could easily integrated into your projects.
and view validation loss and validation accurecy figuers and confusion_matrix figure
and convert final project to keras model (.h5) and then convert to tflite for  android os or to embedded device, like my little Raspberry Pi board 



# Install

```
pip install keras26models
or in colab google cloud
!pip install keras26models
```

## Usage

```
from keras26models import train_model

```

# Examples
```
Reusable Models
Images Classification Transfer learning  
by using CNN 

dataset_path='dataset_path'
img_shape=224
no_class=3
batch_size=16
model_name='mobilenet'
epochs=5
train_model.model_cnn(dataset_path,model_name,epochs,batch_size,no_class,img_shape)

```
# Models List 26

```
1-VGG16
2-VGG19
3-MobilNetv2
4-DenesNet121
5-DenesNet169
6-DenesNet201
7-ResNet101

11-ResNet152v2
12-Xception

20-EfficientNetB3
21-EfficientNetB4
22-EfficientNetB5
23-EfficientNetB6
24-EfficientNetB7
25-MobileNet
26-ResNet50

```
